item.title: GNOME Journal Issue 17 out!
item.description: I’m two days late blogging about the latest release of GNOME Journal (and thanks to Danni for mentioning it!). This is a very special issue written by women in the open source community. It’s the first time we’ve done a themed issue and all articles are by women in the open source community. Also, with the exception of Danni and Stormy who have written for GNOME Journal before, all are first time writers for GJ!
